overview:
Ticketpredator.com is a search engine and comparison resource when it comes to sports, concert and theater tickets.

The search process takes into account the major ticket brokers in the U.S and Canada. The results are presented back to you in a way that makes for easy comparison. Once you make up your mind, it is also possible to buy directly from the ticket broker that you feel suits your needs best.

The site has a concise layout, and you can select the event that interests you via the provided navigation menu.
